# ─── Google OAuth ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your Client ID from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 1. Create a project → APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# 2. Application type: Web application
# 3. Authorised JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173
# 4. Authorised redirect URIs: http://localhost:5173
# 5. Paste the Client ID below and restart the dev server
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here


